data.description: Price Improvement! Discover the perfect blend of convenience and comfort in this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhome/condo nestled in the heart of Twin Falls. With an open concept design, this home welcomes you with a spacious interior that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen boasts ample space with a large island and breakfast bar. Cozy up by the inviting gas fireplace in the living room, complete with brand new carpet throughout all of home. The large master suite is a tranquil retreat, offering a serene space to unwind after a long day.  This home offers practicality with a 2-car garage and RV parking, providing plenty of space for all your vehicles and outdoor toys. A fully fenced and landscaped yard adds privacy and security, ideal for both pets and outdoor gatherings. The home is located on a quiet street close to shopping, schools, and much more.  Whether you're seeking a comfortable family home or a place to entertain and relax, this home offers so much!
